Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:34.99,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,曾经，不久前的非洲深部\NOnce, not long ago,\Nin deepest Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:36.83,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一片繁茂、野性、神奇的热带雨林\Na great rain forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:41.96,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一直鲜为人知\Na wild, magical land,\Nbarely touched by humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这是幽深丛林中特别的一天\NIt's a special day in the dark\Nheart of this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:28.24,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一个新生命诞生\NThere's a new life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一个叫做奥斯卡的小男宝宝\Na precious baby boy named Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:35.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是什么令他如此特殊呢？\NWhat's so special\Nabout this little guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.92,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一些惊人之举即将改变他的一生\NWell, something truly amazing\Nwill transform his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.79,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这就是我们即将讲述的故事\NAnd that's what our\Nstory is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:57.19,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,黑猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在这片热带雨林下面\NBeneath this rain forest canopy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是一个你我从未见过的世界\Nis a world that you or I\Nmay never set eyes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一个没有人烟的地方\NIt's a world with few people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:16.20,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是依旧充满了戏剧、悲伤，和欢乐\Nbut still, it's full of drama,\Nsadness, and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:37.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,《That Man》 by Caro Emerald
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,自从小奥斯卡陪伴他妈妈以来\NAbout three months have passed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,三个月已经过去了\Nsince little Oscar brought\Nlight into his mother's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:57.19,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没有什么让伊沙更开心了\NIsha couldn't be happier\Nwith her new baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.33,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡的世界里始终离不开妈妈\NOscar's world revolves around Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是群里还有35只黑猩猩\Nbut there are 35 other chimpanzees\Nin his group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.37,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们一起组成了一个大家庭\Nthat make a kind of extended family,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.04,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一个不离不弃的大家庭\Nand they're never far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.15,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,或许等到小奥斯卡50岁的时候\NPerhaps one day Oscar will become
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.09,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,也会和他的老爷爷一样\Nan old-timer like Grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.68,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,华发苍颜\Nwho will turn 50 this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是这里也有其他的小孩\NBut there are other kids, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.29,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们将会是小奥斯卡的好伙伴\NThey'll become Oscar's playmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,只有在丛林深处\NIt's a rich society,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.33,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,才会如此的富饶\Nbut in the heart of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.91,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,距离小奥斯卡成年还有20多年\NNow, Oscar won't be\Nin his prime until he's over 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.85,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但总有一天他会长得和这个家伙一样\Nbut one day, he'll look like this big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:05:00.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他叫弗雷迪，一位高大威猛的首领\NThis is Freddy,\Nand he's large and in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他的白胡子显露出\NHis white beard shows his years
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.59,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,丰富的智慧和经验\Nof wisdom and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.23,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在，弗雷迪地位很稳\NRight now, Freddy is untouchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,和其他动物的首领一样\NAnd like most alpha males,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他不能对群里的后来者掉以轻心\Nhe couldn't care less\Nabout the young upstarts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.48,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些晚辈成天想着接过弗雷迪的地位\Nwho would just love\Nto take over his job someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,喂 喂，别想得太远\NYeah, yeah. Seen it all before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:39.36,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在这之前你还是动动脑子如何生存\NYou need brains\Nto make a living in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:41.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,丛林里的工具箱能帮上大忙\NThe jungle toolbox can help,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但你需要知道如何去使用\Nbut only if you're bright\Nenough to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.74,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有时需要家庭教育\NSometimes it just takes\Na little home-schooling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,身边朋友家人的指导\Navailable from your friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:00.08,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,看到了吗？就像这样\NSee? Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.08,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,到手\NRight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:08.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,连鲁弗斯最后也学会了\NEven Rufus catches on, eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,就这样. 虫子被黏在棍棒上.\NThere you go. Bugs on a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:22.20,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡独立的日子来临了\NIt's finally time for Oscar\Nto leave his mother's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:34.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于伊沙的小儿子来说，今天是独立日\NFor Isha 's little boy,\Nthis is independence day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:37.28,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,独立的一小步\Nand independence\Ncomes one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一天独立一点点就足够了\NWell, that's enough\Nindependence for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:19.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一群成年黑星星掌管着奥斯卡的家，\NOscar's forest home is a prime\Npiece of chimpanzee real estate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:23.23,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一片郁郁葱葱却又生存艰难的丛林\Nthat appears rich and lush,\Nbut it's a hard place to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.93,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,丛林本身也是一个富有生机的生命\NThe jungle itself is a living,\Nbreathing thing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.03,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他可不想被活活吃掉\Nthat doesn't want to be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.23,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,寻找食物是主要的工作\NFinding food here is a full-time job
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.03,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,整个家庭成员都要参与\Nthat involves the whole family,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.70,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,包括奥斯卡\Nincluding Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.53,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在他成熟了一点点\NNow that he's grown up a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.04,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他能够自己探路了\Nhe can start to explore on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.28,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是有便车搭 他也不会拒绝\NBut he's not above\Ncatching a lift when he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,真是的，有便车搭为什么还要自己走呢？\NReally, why walk\Nwhen you can hitch a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.92,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,妈妈，快走\NKeep it moving, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪带领着大家寻找午餐\NFreddy leads the search for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.79,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们行动的时候需要有人指引\NIt helps to have someone who\Nknows where they're going,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:23.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,尤其是要找的大餐总不在同一个“餐馆”\Nespecially when the restaurant\Nis never in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:39.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,今天的大餐甚至不在隔壁\NToday the diner isn't even\Nin the same neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,为了寻找水果大餐\NTo find the fruit they'll need,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.68,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们需要穿梭很远\Nthey will have to travel much further
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,中途还需要休息\Nand take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.35,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪知道现在唯一可摘的水果\NFreddy knows the only fruit\Navailable now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,远在他们的领域边缘\Nis on the far side of their kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.63,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这是一个危险的地带\Nout of their safe zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在这块边界上，他们已经战略好几代了\NThis border has been\Na battleground for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.98,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,每个人都高度戒备\NEveryone is on maximum alert
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,小心翼翼地前行\Nand treads as quietly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.89,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪带领着大家靠近敌人\NFreddy is leading them close\Nto their greatest enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这条绵延的山脊\NThis ridge marks the start of territory
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.33,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是对手的领地标志\Nowned by a group\Nof rival chimpanzees.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.57,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,禁果近在咫尺\NThe forbidden fruit is finally in reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.87,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,嘘 奥斯卡 嘘\NShh, Oscar. Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:44.53,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪发现对方要多出一两个人\NFreddy sees his team\Nare outnumbered two to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.17,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们有一个强大的首领\NThe enemy has a formidable leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤\NScar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.90,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤和他的手下\NHe and his team have had Freddy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,盯上弗雷迪已经多年了\Nin their sights for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:04.35,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡紧紧靠着伊沙，他们不敢妄动一步\NOscar clings to Isha.\NThey dare not make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对手已经嗅到了他们气息\NThe rivals have caught their scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:20.20,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡他们已命悬一线\NOscar and the others\Nare in real danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:43.99,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤用猛击发号进攻命令，对于伊沙来说，不跑只有死路一条\NScar's drum is a threat.\NFor Isha, it's run or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.70,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪带着大家逃跑\NFreddy leads the escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.65,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在追赶中冲散弗雷迪的队伍之后\NBy running off Freddy's group,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.16,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤他们宣告小胜一筹\Ntheir enemies have claimed\Na small victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.59,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但这还只是个开始\NBut that's just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.56,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤他们意在拿下整场战争\NScar and his troops are intent\Non winning the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而不仅仅是一场小胜\Nnot just a single battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.90,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,战利品\NThe prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.24,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是弗雷迪家里的一片坚果园\Na grove of nut trees\Nin the center of Freddy's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:34.61,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这块果园是艰险丛林里难得的宝地\NThe grove is an oasis of food\Nin this difficult forest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:37.21,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,如果伤疤他们想要生长壮大\Nand one that Scar's army\Nhas to conquer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:40.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,就必须拿下这块宝地\Nif they're going to survive and thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.63,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙深知伤疤是小奥斯卡最大的威胁\NIsha knows that Scar\Nis the greatest threat to little Oscar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,稍不注意就会引起口角之争\Nand the run-in\Nwas too close for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:05.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,她将尽自己最大的努力保护奥斯卡\NShe'll do everything possible\Nto keep her son safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.92,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡仍需要靠母乳成长\NOscar will rely on his mother's\Nmilk for a good while yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.99,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而伊沙的母乳\Nand to keep that milk flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:29.23,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,依赖着弗雷迪领域里的这片坚果园\NIsha relies on the rich nuts\Nin Freddy's kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:41.70,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这片深受伤疤垂涎的果园\NThe magnificent nut groves,\Nso sought-after by Scar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.15,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,依靠着这里的肥沃土地\Nthrive here because of the rich soil,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,和另一种神奇营养成分\Nand another magic ingredient,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.38,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,生命之泉\Nlife-giving water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:06.50,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在瀑布之下，弗雷迪的领地正中心\NBeneath the waterfall,\Nin the heart of Freddy's territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.19,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,坚果正在成熟\Nthe nuts are coming into season
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.76,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在正是收获的季节\Nand it's time for a feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.98,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些坚果美味可口，营养丰富，令人爱不释手\NThey're delicious, nutritious,\Nand you can't eat just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:31.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一次带很多似乎不现实\NIt seems impossible to have too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是没有袋子你怎么装呢？\NBut how do you carry them\Nwithout a bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.56,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你得动下脑子了\NYou've got to be creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,嗯... 把他们捧在手心\NHmm. Put them over in this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有人见过这个吗？\NAnybody watching this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.21,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,成熟的坚果可以被嗅出来\NThe ripest nuts can be sniffed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.84,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是有些却是很难被敲碎\NBut these are also\Nthe hardest to break into.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:16:00.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们需要合适的工具和正确的方法\NThey require the right tool\Nfor the right job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.80,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,表面上看着很容易\NIt looks easier than it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:21.33,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,实际上需要这些伙计们花费数年才能掌握\Nand the technique takes these\Nguys many years to master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对 就是这样\NYeah, here we go. Yum, yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.35,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有时候打开坚果的最佳办法并不是用工具\NSometimes the best tool\Nfor getting nuts isn't a tool at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没错，有一位好母亲就行了\NYup, it's good old Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,真是笔不错的“交易”\NIt's a pretty sweet deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.30,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是妈妈只能照顾几年的时间\NBut Mom will only help out\Nfor a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:56.57,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,最后他们还是需要自己动手\NThen they'll have to take\Na shot at it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,真的有这么难吗？\NReally, how hard can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.31,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡正在上坚果课\NOscar is in nut preschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.79,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,可是他的锤子有点不对劲\NThere's something wrong\Nwith this hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.95,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这砸不开坚果的！\NIt won't hit the nut!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.46,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问是锤子不行\NYup, definitely the hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.63,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,哈哈 来个更大的！\NOf course. A bigger one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.65,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这是块烂木头!\NThis is defective!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们从来不用已经用过的木头\NThey just don't make logs\Nlike they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:56.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我知道了.肯定是坚果的问题\NAll right. It has to be the nut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:12.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,哈哈  等等  他们是在用石头吗？\NWhoa, whoa, hold on.\NThey're using rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,可是没人告诉他们啊\NNo one said anything about rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:18.85,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,噢，我知道了，他们知道石头更硬\NOh, I get it.\NThey must be harder than wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:33.13,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当坚果遇上石头...\NMr. Nut, meet Mr. Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.40,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,便诞生了“啪啪”\NCome to Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:44.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,好极了！敲开一个\NYes! Okay, that's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡的坚果吃光了\NNow Oscar's out of nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.53,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他需要丢下锤子去进货\NHe'll have to leave\Nhis hammer to stock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.46,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,菜鸟错误\NRookie mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:03.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我盯你小子一天了\NI had an eye on that kid all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:05.99,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,傻小子\NWhat an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.88,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,坚果大餐过后，\NAfter all those nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.58,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没人在丛林里摇晃\Nnobody's swinging through the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:25.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没错，现在是好好休息消化的时间\NYes, it's time to rest and digest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.92,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,连我们的小奥斯卡都呼呼大睡\NEven our boy Oscar's knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.93,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,饱餐之后需要休息好几个小时\NIt can take hours\Nto sleep off a big meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.70,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是丛林仍旧生机勃勃\Nbut the jungle never rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.46,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,正午当头的时候\NIn the heat of day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:07.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,父母们只想享受一下宁静的生活\Nthe parents just want a few\Nminutes of peace and quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.80,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是孩子们可不这么想\Nbut the kids have other ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.67,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,特别是奥斯卡\NEspecially Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.40,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,来吧，伙伴们！\NCome on up, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:31.35,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这里有数不清的树\NA million trees in this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你要怎么玩过我\Nand you have to play over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:45.26,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我还在睡觉 我还在睡觉!\NI'm sleeping. I am still sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:23.30,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,看看多么宓囊辽\NPoor Isha. Just look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,可怜她一手紧紧的抓着奥斯卡\NShe really does have\Nher hands full with Oscar,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.67,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是她的耐心却是相当足\Nbut her patience\Nnever seems to run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:33.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡是只幸运的黑猩猩\NOscar's one lucky young chimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤和他的那群暴徒日益临近\NScar and his thugs\Nare a growing threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.57,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,食物在他的领地里依旧稀贵\NFood is still scarce in their territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.91,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,如果一切照旧\NIf nothing changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:05.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们将被迫离开果园\Nthey'll be forced to make\Na move on the nut groves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:08.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,如果成功\NIf they succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:10.48,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪他们将被驱逐\NFreddy and his group will be exiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:13.15,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,永远从这里消失\Nfrom their homeland forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:20.92,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,渐老的伤疤一直受到群内的压力\NThe aging Scar is under\Nconstant pressure from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:24.40,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他群里的雄性黑猩猩都很强\NThe males in his team are so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:27.30,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,随便哪一个都可能取代他\Nthat any one of them could\Nchallenge him as leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.37,0:22:28.97,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他也深知这点\Nand he knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.85,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,等级制度维系着种群的和睦\NGrooming helps hold\Nthis volatile team together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:38.88,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,也提醒着每位成员谁才是老大\Nand reminds everyone who's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:42.65,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没有这点，他们将是一盘散沙\NWithout it, there would be anarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:00.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,等级制度短期还不会变\NThis hierarchy may hold\Nin the short term,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是伤疤还能撑多久呢？\Nbut how long can Scar\Ncount on his men?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:13.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,远在西边\NFar to the west,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:17.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,瀑布下面一种奇异的果子已经成熟\Na special fruit has come into\Nseason beneath the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:20.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,沙克格劳荻斯（音译）\NSacoglottis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:21.53,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,连说三遍看看\NTrying saying that three times fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.26,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪知道果子的价值\NFreddy knows the fruit is a real bonus,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.83,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,因此，最好是充分利用它\Nso it's best to make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:38.74,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙为自己和奥斯卡收集了一堆果子\NIsha collects a private stash\Nfor herself and Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:53.79,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,记得吃前要洗洗\NRemember to wash your food\Nbefore eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:05.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,然后，就可以嚼成浆了\NOnce washed,\Nthe fruit is chewed to a pulp
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:08.00,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这样所有的养分都能被汲取出来\Nso all the goodness can be sucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:12.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没有牙齿也能照样吃，难怪老爷爷如此喜欢！\NYou can do it without teeth.\NNo wonder Grandpa likes them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:14.94,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这吃相不错\NThat's a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:17.85,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,老爷爷和大家一起其乐融融的场景并不多见\NNot a lot of family photos\Nwith Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:20.21,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,很开胃口\NVery appetizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.66,0:24:24.65,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,果子被吸干后\NWhen the fruit is sucked dry,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.72,0:24:26.35,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,浸一下还可以继续\Nrinse and repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.76,0:24:32.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,哇 真是不错的好果子！\NWow, that is some good Sacoglottis!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:50.01,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这回小奥斯卡终于不需要妈妈的帮忙了\NFinally, this is something Oscar can\Neat without his mother's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.08,0:24:53.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是没人知道吃了这顿，下顿会在哪里\NBut it's anyone's guess where\Nthe next meal is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.23,0:25:06.20,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,随着果子渐少\NWith the fruit running low,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:09.67,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪一大家旅游到另一个果园\NFreddy's family resorts\Nto another source of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:13.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,和我们一样，他们也爱吃水果、蔬菜和肉类\NLike us, they eat fruits,\Nvegetables, and meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.44,0:25:18.50,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是他们吃的肉可能会吓你一跳\NBut their choice in meat is something\Nthat just might surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.80,0:25:43.17,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,猴子\NMonkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.87,0:25:48.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,雄性负责狩猎\NThe males take up the hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.77,0:25:50.26,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们分开\NThey split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.71,0:25:52.23,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在林中摆好阵\NFanning out through the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.31,0:25:54.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,各司其职\Nthey take up their places.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.15,0:25:57.17,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪在中间\NFreddy is at center stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.82,0:26:04.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡和伊沙在一旁策应\NOscar and Isha watch\Nfrom the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.20,0:26:13.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些髯猴（产于非洲）成了猎物\NThese colobus monkeys\Nare being hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.80,0:26:17.27,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,由于体型比黑猩猩灵巧\NSmaller and lighter\Nthan the chimpanzees,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.34,0:26:19.36,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们可以在小树枝间穿梭\Nthey can run on thinner branches,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.44,0:26:22.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这使得狩猎更富挑战性\Nand this makes the hunt\Nmuch more challenging.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.28,0:26:31.48,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪隐藏起来\NFreddy holds back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.55,0:26:33.11,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没有计划是不行的\NThis operation requires planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.19,0:26:35.25,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而且每个人都要出力\Nand everyone has a role to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.93,0:26:44.99,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们一个个的悄悄就位\NOne by one,\Nthey silently take their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.17,0:26:54.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,猴子们还没注意到他们\NThe monkeys still haven't seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.32,0:27:04.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在，一个先锋已经上阵\NNow, the blockers move up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.89,0:27:12.86,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们爬到一个显眼的位置\NThey're supposed to be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.93,0:27:14.83,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,想引起猴子的注意\Nand take a position in clear view.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.97,0:27:20.56,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,另一个先锋\NAnother blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.07,0:27:22.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,堵死了另一条出口\NAnother escape route closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.31,0:27:29.27,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪渐渐逼近\NFreddy climbs carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.81,0:27:31.57,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他必须隐蔽好自己\NHe must not be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.82,0:27:39.31,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,作为一个埋伏者\NAs ambusher,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.39,0:27:42.48,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪在发动进攻前必须悄无声息\NFreddy will stay hidden\Nuntil he makes the grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.70,0:27:52.93,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,完美\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.57,0:28:00.30,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在，轮到驱赶者了\NNow, for the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.37,0:28:03.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他要把猴子赶到伏击者那边\NHe'll push the monkeys\Ntowards the ambusher.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.70,0:28:24.86,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,预备\NReady,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:26.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,稳住\Nsteady,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:29.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,进攻！\Ngo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.35,0:28:40.94,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,抓住了一只!\NThey've got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.75,0:28:49.15,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪抢了一块最好的肉\NFreddy takes the best for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.33,0:28:55.16,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一轮哄抢过后\NAfter the initial scramble,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.23,0:28:57.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们才坐下来慢慢细品\Nthe group settles in for the feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.73,0:29:04.76,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于奥斯卡来说，应该在大人的桌上为自己争个位子\NFor Oscar, it's time to try to\Nwin a seat at the adult table.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.97,0:29:07.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在狩猎中出力的成员先得到肉\NShares get dished out first to those
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.67,0:29:10.67,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,帮了忙的也能得到奖赏\Nthat helped in the hunt\Nor as payback for favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.74,0:29:12.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是无论如何\NBut no matter how hard you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.85,0:29:15.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,总有些人觉得自己被蒙骗了\Nthere's always someone\Nwho feels shortchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.22,0:29:24.31,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,雌性这时不会大意\NThe females couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.39,0:29:27.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当她们面对想蹭肉的雄猩猩时，\NWhen it comes\Nto guarding meat from the guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.09,0:29:29.06,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,姑娘们总能赢\Ngirl power usually wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.76,0:29:33.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,走开, 大块头\NBack up, big boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.58,0:29:46.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,饭后来点纤维是最好不过了\NIt's always good to add\Na little fiber to your diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.61,0:29:48.84,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,所以别忘了旁边的色拉\Nso don't forget the side salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.50,0:30:04.83,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,和往常一样，奥斯卡排在最后\NAs usual, Oscar was last in line,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.90,0:30:07.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,错失了大餐\Nso he missed the main course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.33,0:30:09.93,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他还在吃奶\NHe'll have to settle\Nfor his mother's milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.00,0:30:13.30,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,或许他不是大家最喜欢的小孩\NHe may not be the most popular\Nlittle boy with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.37,0:30:16.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是他总能得到妈妈的关爱\Nbut his mother's love\Nis something he can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.62,0:30:29.71,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,黄昏来临, 美洲豹在地上开始搜寻\NWith dusk approaching, leopards will\Nsoon prowl the forest floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.79,0:30:31.88,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,如果伊沙和奥斯卡想睡得安稳，\NIf Isha and Oscar want to sleep safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.96,0:30:33.98,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,唯一的办法就是往上爬\Nthe only way is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:57.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些小树枝可以织成床垫\NYoung, flexible branches\Ncan be woven into a platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.19,0:31:08.39,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,树叶可以拿来垫上\NAnd leaves from the same tree\Nwill do for bedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.61,0:31:28.58,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,真舒服\NNow, that's comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.49,0:31:41.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,和其他小孩一样，奥斯卡不愿睡觉\NLike most kids, Oscar hates bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.35,0:32:06.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,最终，伊沙的小淘气捅破了麻布袋\NFinally, Isha 's little rascal hits the sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.47,0:32:26.50,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,即使小孩不吵了\NEven if the kids let you sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.57,0:32:30.03,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,邻居们还是喋喋不休\Nthere's a good chance\Nthe neighbors will keep you awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.68,0:32:37.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,唉，拜托...\NAh, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.39,0:32:46.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了行吗？\NAre you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.46,0:32:51.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你知道青蛙也是可以吃的\NYou know, frogs are edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.70,0:33:00.00,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,看我的\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.42,0:33:52.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙和奥斯卡沿着奇路而下\NIsha and Oscar go downstairs\Nthe exciting way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.44,0:34:06.90,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一清早，吃完饭后，\NEarly morning, just after breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.97,0:34:11.38,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是相互梳理，培养感情的最佳时刻\Nis the best time of day to strengthen\Nfriendships with a little grooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.25,0:34:23.98,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪群里的友谊比以前更加重要了\NThe bonds between Freddy's team\Nare more important than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.49,0:34:28.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们远比伤疤的种群小\NThe group is far smaller\Nthan Scar's rival army
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.49,0:34:30.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而团队精神是他们保卫坚果园，\Nand teamwork is their best chance
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.60,0:34:34.16,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,保障后代生存的关键\Nof protecting the nut groves\Nfor the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.51,0:34:44.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡的未来就在他们手里\NOscar's future is in all their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.85,0:34:55.81,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,远在东边，弗雷迪的领地里\NFar to the east,\Njust inside Freddy's territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.95,0:34:57.89,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一颗无花果数结满了无花果\Na fig tree comes into fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.96,0:35:00.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,每个人都想要\Nand is an instant hit with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.13,0:35:04.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,无花果是丛林里的救命草\NFigs are a lifeline in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.30,0:35:06.26,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,总在没有食物的时候结果\Noften fruiting when\Nthere is nothing else to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.93,0:35:37.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤一伙正在准备突袭\NScar's gang is mounting a raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.43,0:35:42.09,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们吃光了自己家的所有果子\NThey've wiped out the fruit\Nin their own territory
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.17,0:35:45.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,饥饿难当，他们越过了边界\Nand have crossed the border\Nto satisfy their hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.57,0:35:47.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,所有的动物都在让路\NAll other animals scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.62,0:36:01.71,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,即使这些无花果也只够他们吃一阵子\NEven these figs\Nwon't keep them fed for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.79,0:36:03.98,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这只是个权宜之计\NThis is just a stepping stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.76,0:36:06.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,等时机成熟时\NWhen the moment is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.59,0:36:09.03,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们将要夺过真正的奖励，\Nthey will try to take over the real prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.09,0:36:10.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,坚果园\Nthe nut groves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.44,0:36:18.99,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤准备在东面发起突袭\NScar's raid on the eastern border
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.07,0:36:21.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪他们毫无察觉\Ngoes unnoticed by Freddy's group.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.41,0:36:25.57,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,坚果园里又有一种新的坚果成熟了\NA new kind of nut is ripening\Nin the nut groves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.64,0:36:27.67,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些坚果比上次的更硬\NThese are far tougher\Nthan the last ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.75,0:36:30.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是时候动用重型装备了\NIt's time to bring in\Nthe heavy equipment,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.75,0:36:32.91,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,强大的工具!\Npower tools!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.67,0:36:50.57,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,锤子的质量直接决定了能否打开坚果\NSuccess with these nuts\Nis all about the quality of your hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.94,0:36:56.74,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当他们离开捡坚果时，你可以偷偷窃取\NYou can steal someone else's\Nwhile they're off collecting nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.78,0:37:02.80,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪就是这方面的专家\NAnd Freddy is an expert at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.88,0:37:05.98,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是对工具别太粗暴\NBut, man, is he tough on his tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.05,0:37:09.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些可是公共财产\NThese things are\Na community resource,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.39,0:37:12.59,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,所以能不能别搞破坏？\Nso can you please\Ntry not to break them?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.64,0:37:26.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,安全第一!\NSafety first!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.14,0:37:29.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,注意保持手脚和石头的距离\NSo please keep hands and feet\Nclear of rocks at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.72,0:37:42.88,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,黑猩猩在这里已经砸了4000多年的坚果了\NChimps have gathered here\Nto crack nuts for over 4, 000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.69,0:37:48.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,砸坚果已经成了他们的文化遗产之一\NNut-cracking is\Npart of the group's cultural heritage
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.29,0:37:50.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一代代薪火相传\Nand is passed through the generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.53,0:37:53.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,特别是母子相传\Nespecially from mother to child.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.47,0:37:58.20,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于奥斯卡来说，学习是一个漫长的过程\NLearning, for Oscar,\Nwill be a slow process.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.24,0:38:01.90,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,拿起一块这样的石头都需要花费他好几年时间\NIt will be years before he could\Neven lift a rock like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.78,0:38:06.94,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,教育他如何在丛林里生存\NDay after day,\Nit takes a committed mom to teach him
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.01,0:38:09.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是他妈妈的长期义务\Nhow to make a living in the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.25,0:38:46.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙的儿子自力更生还需要好几年\NIt will be many years\Nbefore Isha 's son can fend for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.82,0:39:24.81,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一场风暴让伤疤他们兴奋不已\NA gathering storm\Nexcites Scar's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.59,0:39:56.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是对于弗雷迪他们来说，风暴不是什么好事\NFor Freddy's gang,\Nthe rain is less welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.29,0:39:59.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,黑猩猩讨厌潮湿\NChimps just hate getting wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.68,0:40:21.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡抱着伊沙取暖\NOscar gets all the warmth\Nhe can from Isha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.28,0:40:52.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤他们一伙\NScar and his gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.59,0:41:03.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,风暴给了他们很好的掩护\NThe storm is cover for a raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.12,0:41:36.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这次他们把弗雷迪一伙逼入绝境\NThis time, they've got them cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.40,0:41:51.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙和奥斯卡陷入了危机\NIsha and Oscar are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.29,0:42:14.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤军队势不可挡\NScar's army was overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.37,0:42:24.36,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡他们零零散散，军心动摇\NOscar's group is in disarray\Nand badly shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.78,0:42:39.94,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,混乱之中，奥斯卡和母亲走散了\NIn all the chaos,\NOscar lost contact with his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.35,0:42:44.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,到处不见伊沙的身影\NIsha is nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.92,0:43:16.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙被伤疤他们打伤，不知道逃到了哪里\NIsha has been injured and separated\Nfrom the group by Scar's gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.76,0:43:19.28,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,她会努力安全归来\NShe will struggle to get back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.66,0:43:26.56,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,孤独的丛林是如此的凄凉\NThis is no forest\Nto be alone in after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.51,0:43:44.38,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙的好几个朋友在走离种群的安全区之后\NSeveral of Isha 's friends\Nhave been lost to leopards,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.45,0:43:48.08,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,落入了美洲豹的口中\Noften when they have strayed\Nfrom the safety of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.21,0:44:51.71,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙再也不会回来了\NIsha will never return to her family
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.05,0:44:54.95,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,或者回到奥斯卡身边\Nor her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.93,0:45:09.76,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡不知道他的妈妈已经逝去\NOscar doesn't know\Nabout his mother's death
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.47,0:45:12.37,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他仍旧到处找妈妈\Nand he searches for her everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.98,0:45:23.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,随着时间流逝，他渐渐感到了孤单\NWith every hour that slips by,\Nhe becomes more desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.70,0:45:42.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡处于长身体的时期\NOscar's growing body\Nneeds constant food.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.10,0:45:46.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他努力回忆着当初妈妈是怎么谋生的\NHe tries to remember\Nwhat his mom did to make their living.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.17,0:45:49.20,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是没有她帮忙什么也干不了\NBut nothing comes easily without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.60,0:46:14.39,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,日子一天天过去\NHours turn into days.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.13,0:46:17.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡不能再花太多时间寻找了\NOscar must spend less time searching
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.74,0:46:20.36,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他必须花时间想办法谋生\Nand more time focusing on his survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.34,0:47:32.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,饥饿驱使着奥斯卡来到一个蜜蜂窝前\NHunger drives Oscar to a bees' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.31,0:47:37.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,蜂蜜是绝佳的食物，但是他以前总是依赖妈妈取蜂蜜\NHoney is good food, but he's always\Nrelied on his mom to collect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.39,0:47:48.79,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于小手来说，洞穴太深，而且蜜蜂们很不友善\NThe honey's too deep for small arms to\Nreach, and the bees are not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.53,0:47:58.26,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡的短板却是弗雷迪的优势\NOscar's loss will be Freddy's gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.99,0:48:22.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,首领拿到了一块最大的蜂蜜\NThe boss takes the biggest\Npiece of honeycomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.39,0:48:24.33,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,人人都有份\Nbut there's enough left\Nfor everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.36,0:48:28.80,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,除了发现它的小奥斯卡\Nexcept the little boy who found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.48,0:48:41.04,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于一只年轻饥饿的小黑猩猩来说\NThe forest seems an\Nincreasingly hostile place
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.11,0:48:43.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,丛林变得越来越充满敌意\Nfor a young, hungry chimpanzee.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.75,0:48:50.85,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些口齿锋利的蚂蚁军团\NThe razor-sharp jaws\Nof these army ants
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.92,0:48:54.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,几分钟之内能剥光一个无花果或是蜥蜴的皮\Ncan strip a frog or a lizard\Nto the bone in minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.29,0:48:59.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,把那些能吃掉你的东西当成食物是个好主意吗？\NIs it really a good idea to eat\Nsomething that can eat you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.94,0:49:12.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡是第一个被咬的\NOscar is the first to get bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.48,0:49:15.88,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没有妈妈，他必须尽快从富有经验的长辈那里学习\NWithout a mother, he'll need to learn\Nfast from the older chimps.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.65,0:49:19.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,总的来说，第一步，\NAll right, step one,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.58,0:49:23.08,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,取手边的树枝做成一个微型钓鱼竿\Nmake a miniature fishing rod\Nfrom a nearby branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:29.02,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,第二步，丢进去等上钩\NStep two, cast it in and wait for a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.69,0:49:33.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,最后, 第三步, 满竿的蚂蚁!\NAnd finally, step three, ants on a stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.83,0:49:35.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,尽情享用吧!\NEat and enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.31,0:49:44.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,小伙子，吃得真香啊！\NBoy! That is spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.05,0:49:55.38,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,真是天才!\NIt's ingenious!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.45,0:49:56.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,蚂蚁会咬你的嘴唇,\NThey will bite your lips,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.62,0:49:59.15,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但你身上其他的地方还是很安全的\Nbut at least the rest of you is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.67,0:50:11.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡远远躲开\NOscar keeps his distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.27,0:50:15.71,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,或许吸取经验之后下次会更安全\NMaybe it's safer\Njust to pick up tips for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.36,0:50:39.09,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡瘦得很快\NOscar is losing weight quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.16,0:50:40.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没有人收留他，\Nand with no one to groom him,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.67,0:50:42.16,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,日子变得越发难熬\Nit's becoming harder to keep ticks
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.23,0:50:44.36,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,身上的虫子也越来越多\Nand other bugs from his skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.31,0:50:52.83,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,是时候面对现实了\NIt's time to accept the simple truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.61,0:50:55.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伊沙不会回来了\NIsha isn't coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.68,0:50:58.91,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡需要一位新妈妈\NOscar has to find a new mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.42,0:51:05.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但不幸的是，大部分的雌猩猩都有自己的孩子了\NBut sadly for him, most of the\Nfemales have kids of their own
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.49,0:51:07.72,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,也帮不上什么忙\Nand are unable to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.74,0:51:20.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一次又一次，奥斯卡被拒绝\NAgain and again, Oscar is rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.42,0:51:36.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,即使是找个朋友也变得艰难\NEven finding a friend seems hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.78,0:52:05.27,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,形影相吊\NIt's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.05,0:52:10.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤他们那天夺走的或许不止一条生命\NScar and his men may have\Ntaken more than one life that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.96,0:52:49.09,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,敌人又回来了\NThe enemy has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.16,0:52:51.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们又吃光了家里的果子\NThey have eaten all the food\Nin their own territory
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.83,0:52:54.80,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在正准备偷取弗雷迪家的果子，来维持种群的壮大\Nand are now stealing from Freddy's\Nland to sustain their number.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.77,0:53:06.04,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于伤疤来说，群里没有一个好人\NFor Scar, it's no more Mr. Nice Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.65,0:53:14.74,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们越来越没耐心了\NThere is a growing impatience\Namong Scar's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.55,0:53:17.89,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,总是想着占领果园\NThey want to take the nut groves,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.06,0:53:22.72,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,不止一个人想造反夺权\Nand more than one of them\Nwould like to be leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.82,0:53:47.31,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡使尽了浑身解数\NOscar has tried everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.39,0:53:49.25,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但他仍旧单身一人\Nbut he is still alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.33,0:53:59.23,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,还有最后一只黑猩猩他没接近过\NThere's only one chimp\Nhe hasn't approached.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.70,0:54:00.89,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪\NFreddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.78,0:54:18.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,跟着首领，\NBy following the leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.25,0:54:21.08,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡至少能找到最好的食物，\NOscar will at least find the best food
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.15,0:54:23.45,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,明白什么东西能吃\Nand work out what's safe to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.36,0:54:27.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在，生存才是关键\NRight now, survival is all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.80,0:54:38.39,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪不是一个很有耐心的人，\NFreddy is not known for his tolerance,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.40,0:54:41.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是奥斯卡也不是存心想找茬\Nbut Oscar isn't a challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.31,0:54:45.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这对他们两人都是一段奇妙的经历\NThis will be\Na new experience for them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.05,0:54:59.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一个温婉的收留是奥斯卡再也期待不过的了\NA gentle acceptance is more than\NOscar could have hoped for.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.66,0:55:08.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,和弗雷迪在一起\NBeing at Freddy's side
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.17,0:55:11.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他能学到一些准备食物的经验\Nshould allow him to pick up some\Ntips on food preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.05,0:55:23.81,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,或许大块头的餐桌礼仪\NMaybe the big guy's table manners
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.88,0:55:26.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,没有树立最好的榜样\Ndon't set the best example,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.25,0:55:28.48,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是谁来告诉他呢？\Nbut who's going to tell him off
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.29,0:55:31.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,和他身边的朋友吵一架?\Nor pick a fight\Nwith the friend sitting next to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.41,0:56:27.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,日子一天天过去\NAs the days pass, Freddy and Oscar's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.85,0:56:30.18,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪和奥斯卡的关系一直没有什么变化\Nrelationship begins to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.98,0:56:33.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,直至一件特殊的事情发生\NUntil something\Nextraordinary happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.12,0:56:37.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪允许奥斯卡骑在他的背上\NFreddy allows Oscar\Nto ride on his back
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.82,0:56:40.05,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,通常只有妈妈才会这样\Nas usually only a mother would.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.27,0:56:55.20,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这蕴含了一种令人非常难以置信的情感\NIt's a sign of something truly incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.34,0:56:59.61,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪收养了奥斯卡\NFreddy will adopt Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.46,0:57:20.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,给奥斯卡坚果不会有什么帮助，\NJust being led to these nuts\Nwould not help Oscar,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.43,0:57:23.09,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但现在弗雷迪来了，\Nbut now Freddy steps up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.17,0:57:26.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他总把自己砸的坚果先分给新朋友奥斯卡\Nand gives his new friend first pick\Nof every one he cracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.50,0:57:28.67,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,就像他曾经的母亲一样\Njust as his mother once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.74,0:57:31.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们的关系越来越好\NThe bond between them is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.97,0:57:58.80,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这是奥斯卡吃得最香氛的一顿了，自从伊沙消失以来\NIt's Oscar's best meal\Nsince Isha vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.51,0:58:10.71,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,种群正等着首领发话，\NThe group is waiting for their leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.78,0:58:12.91,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是弗雷迪有他自己的打算\Nbut Freddy has a new project.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.69,0:58:20.99,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡成为孤儿后不久，\NThe learning that stopped short\Nwhen Oscar was orphaned
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.06,0:58:22.72,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,又重拾了昔日的学业\Nis starting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.39,0:58:27.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,跟着一位聪明熟练的黑猩猩学习\NHe's with a wise and skilled\Nchimpanzee who has much to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.16,0:58:55.65,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,会议之后继续开讲\NForest school is back in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.83,0:59:06.46,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪走到哪，奥斯卡跟到哪\NEverywhere Freddy goes,\NOscar follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.44,0:59:14.84,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪做什么，奥斯卡跟着做什么\NAnd everything Freddy does,\NOscar copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.92,0:59:27.55,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我们的小家伙快速掌握着丛林法则\NOur little boy is\Non the fast track to forest knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.17,0:59:45.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有了新朋友之后，弗雷迪的生活更加丰富多彩\NFreddy's world may be richer,\Nthanks to his new friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.81,0:59:50.08,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是担负起了照顾奥斯卡的义务，使得他无暇顾及领土大权\Nbut his commitment to Oscar has left\Nhim no time to patrol his borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.55,0:59:54.68,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这一点被某人发现了\NThe change has been noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.53,1:00:10.06,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤他们现在穿过了边界\NScar and his gang have now\Ncrossed over the ridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.13,1:00:14.33,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们通常不会这么容易就踏进弗雷迪的领土\NThey would not usually get this deep\Ninto Freddy's land without opposition
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.41,1:00:17.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们打算好好把握这个机会\Nand they intend to take full advantage.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.65,1:00:27.64,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,部队在前进之前需要先补给一下\NThe troops need to refuel\Nbefore they push on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.09,1:00:31.61,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,一颗巨大的无花果树遭到掠夺\NThe grand fig tree is being pillaged.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.52,1:00:36.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这是弗雷迪家族赖以生存的食物\NThis is the food\Nthat Freddy's group were relying on,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.23,1:00:41.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是伤疤可管不了那么多\Nbut Scar has no interest\Nin the needs of his enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.87,1:00:47.74,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,轻而易举的入侵之后，\NEncouraged by the lack\Nof resistance at the border,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.81,1:00:51.00,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,掠夺者在弗雷迪的领地更加肆意\Nthe intruders are now\Ndeep inside Freddy's land.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.61,1:00:56.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是队伍里的异议渐起\NBut there is growing dissent\Nin the ranks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.28,1:01:00.81,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这支队伍的作战能力毋庸置疑\NThe physical power of\Nthis army is beyond question,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.88,1:01:03.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是整个团队也容易打散\Nbut the unity of a team can be fragile.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.89,1:01:06.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤需要提防着背后\NScar needs to watch his back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.44,1:01:27.88,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪全身心地投入到奥斯卡身上\NFreddy has become\Ncompletely devoted to Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.38,1:01:32.37,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,最高级的雄性为最低级的梳理毛发\NThe highest-ranking male\Ngrooming the lowest.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.52,1:01:35.95,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这真是一个令人吃惊的转变\NIt's an astonishing turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.38,1:02:07.11,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,数周之前，奥斯卡一无所有\NA few weeks ago, Oscar had nothing,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.55,1:02:10.71,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,现在吃得好，有人疼\Nand now he is well fed\Nand completely adored,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.36,1:02:15.29,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而救他的人却是大家都没想到的\Nand his savior is the last one\Nanyone could have expected.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.24,1:03:00.43,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对手吃饱也休息好了\NThe rivals are fed and rested.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.14,1:03:09.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤和他那群暴徒掌控着坚果园\NScar and his mob\Nare within reach of the nut groves.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.55,1:03:15.68,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,全面围攻的时候到了\NThe time for a full invasion has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.06,1:03:59.05,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪给他的同伴梳理毛发\NFreddy grooms his allies.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.73,1:04:02.49,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他知道麻烦正在靠近\NHe knows there is trouble approaching
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.57,1:04:06.16,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这是他第一次紧张了好几周\Nand for the first time\Nin weeks, he appears nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.14,1:04:17.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,友谊需要时间投入，他的注意力开始转移\NFriendships need investment,\Nand his attention has been elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.08,1:04:24.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡注意到了这点\NOscar feels Freddy's focus\Ndrift away from him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.29,1:04:31.28,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪必须让队员明白他还是老大\NFreddy must reassure his team\Nthat he is still the boss
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.36,1:04:34.52,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他有能力把大家凝聚在一起\Nand has the strength\Nto unite them and lead them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.44,1:04:44.13,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡有点不解\NOscar is confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.21,1:04:47.97,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他已经失去了一位母亲，似乎又要失去一位父亲\NHe's lost one parent and\Nseems to be losing another.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.48,1:05:20.27,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对手正在逼近\NThe rivals are close.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.62,1:05:32.78,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡他们感觉到了不对劲\NOscar and the group\Nsense that something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.37,1:05:49.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪有所察觉\NSomething catches Freddy's eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.12,1:06:00.91,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤发起了进攻\NScar attacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.56,1:06:06.25,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,最后一战已经打响\NThe final push has begun.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.20,1:06:21.40,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪他们不能就此逃跑\NFreddy's team can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.41,1:06:28.90,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们必须迎面而上\NThey have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.98,1:06:31.21,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而这时伤疤他们中有人却开始退缩\NBut some of Scar's mob hold back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.62,1:06:38.61,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪引领进攻\NFreddy leads the attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.33,1:06:51.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,两个首领一对一单挑\NFreddy and Scar go head-to-head.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.48,1:07:05.61,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,胜者只有一个\NThere can be only one victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.21,1:07:32.14,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪的鼓声宣告了胜利\NFreddy's drum announces victory.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.48,1:07:40.94,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,伤疤短期内不会再来了\NScar will not be returning\Nanytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.12,1:07:45.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,团队协作战胜了蛮力攻击\NTeamwork has beaten brute force.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.62,1:08:04.62,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,几个月之后
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.47,1:08:35.06,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,队伍正在壮大\NThe group is now thriving,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.14,1:08:38.77,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们拥有坚果园的绝对主权\Nunchallenged in their\Nownership of the precious nut groves.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.55,1:08:44.34,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,坚果课继续进行，\NCracking school continues,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.41,1:08:46.81,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是有些学生怎么也学不会\Nbut some students\Nnever seem to catch on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.49,1:08:54.96,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,老爷爷亲眼目睹了伤疤的大败，\NGrandpa has lived\Nto see Scar dealt a blow
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.03,1:08:57.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,或许至此他再也无力东山再起\Nfrom which he may never recover.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.16,1:09:03.13,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡仍旧麻烦不断\NAnd Oscar is causing\Nas much trouble as ever,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.97,1:09:06.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是现在他完全融入了大家庭，\Nbut now he's fully\Naccepted by the group,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.74,1:09:09.37,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,成为了每个人的好朋友\Nand seems to be\Neveryone's new friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.41,1:09:18.58,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,或许他们从此过上了恬静的生活\NMaybe quiet times are returning at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.39,1:09:24.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡和弗雷迪\NOscar and Freddy\Nhave been transformed
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.39,1:09:26.82,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在最后几个月的动乱中都得到了转变\Nby the turmoil of the last few months.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.86,1:09:31.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于奥斯卡来说，他妈妈的逝去本意味着结束\NFor Oscar, the loss of his\Nmother could have meant the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.50,1:09:33.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是一个最意外的收养\NInstead, it's a new beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.80,1:09:36.96,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,给了他一个崭新的开始\Nwith the most unlikely foster parent\Nin the forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.70,1:09:40.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而弗雷迪呢?\NAnd Freddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.60,1:09:42.09,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他发现自己也有温柔的一面\NHe's discovered a softer side
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.17,1:09:44.66,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这一面一定隐藏了很久\Nthat must have been there all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.19,1:10:04.22,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有了弗雷迪的保护，\NSecure in Freddy's arms,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.29,1:10:07.59,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡的未来一片光明\Nthe future finally looks bright for Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.60,1:10:30.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,《That Man》 by Caro Emerald
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.77,1:11:58.97,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当这个大块头决定收留这个小孤儿，\NWhen this big male decided\Nto carry this little orphan
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.04,1:12:01.07,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,照顾他，抚养他时，\Nand take care of him and give him food,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.14,1:12:03.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这逐渐令人叹为观止\Nit literally took our breath away.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.95,1:12:06.44,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当然，毫无疑问\NFor sure, there's no doubt
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.52,1:12:08.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他拯救了一个小生命\Nhe saved the life of the little one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.69,1:12:11.28,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这一幕真的很感人\NAnd that was really\Nvery touching to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.06,1:12:15.42,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当你看到一位妈妈背着她的孩子时，\NAnd when you see a\Nmother carrying its baby,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.49,1:12:16.75,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,真的很温馨.\Nit's charming.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.83,1:12:19.89,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是当你看到金刚一样的大块头\NBut when you see this huge,\NKing Kong-like figure
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.96,1:12:23.30,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,背着一个弱小的男孩到处转悠时，\Ncarrying this tiny, little,\Nmale orphan around,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.37,1:12:24.46,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,真的很可爱.\Nit was lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.90,1:12:28.10,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,对于他们俩来说\NEvery single day\Nwas an act of beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.17,1:12:30.11,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,每一天都是美丽的\Nbetween the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.17,1:12:32.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这些让人无法忘怀\NAnd that's something\Nyou can never forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.41,1:12:36.97,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有时我会想\NSometimes I imagine
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.05,1:12:38.54,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,当世界上所有的人\Nthe rest of the world waking up,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.62,1:12:41.74,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,都忙着乘公交，乘地铁上班时，\Ngetting on busses,\Nor they may be getting on subways.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.82,1:12:45.41,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我们的工作就是在丛林中步行一小时，\NOur commute to work\Nis walking for an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.49,1:12:47.65,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,追寻黑猩猩的足迹\Nthrough the jungle\Nto find chimpanzees.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.72,1:12:50.72,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有些树木令人很难忍受\NSome of this stuff is just impenetrable
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.79,1:12:53.92,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,有些灌木丛很难穿梭过去\Nand really difficult to move through.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.10,1:12:59.73,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但走在这片丛林里真的很幸福\NIt really is a joy\Nto walk through this forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.64,1:13:05.51,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,你看，并不总是那么容易\NYou see, it's not always that easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.58,1:13:07.48,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我们只有埋头继续前进...\NSo, we're just walking...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.98,1:13:16.61,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,他们在显眼的地方叮你\NThey bite you\Nin the most remarkable places.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.02,1:13:20.35,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这群蜂快把我逼疯了\NThese sweat bees are driving me nuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.42,1:13:22.91,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,而且，他们不是小蜜蜂\NStill, at least they're not honeybees.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.99,1:13:26.69,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,啊！啊！啊！\NAhh! Ow! Ow! Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.40,1:13:32.13,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,让人有点受不了了\NIt's gotten intolerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.20,1:13:33.19,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,我要走了\NI'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.50,1:13:35.03,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,噢，我的天呐！\NOh, my God. Ed!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.71,1:13:37.87,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,如果被咬上一口，你就死定了.\NIf it bites you, you won't survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.68,1:13:41.04,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,这可不是在野餐.\NIt's not a picnic, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.22,1:13:48.24,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,很好!\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.49,1:13:53.32,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,肯定还有一条稍简单的路\NThere must be easier ways\Nto make a living,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.02,1:13:56.12,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,但是也不会好到哪里去\Nbut they're not as much fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.50,1:14:18.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,《Rise》 by Mcclain Sisters
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.70,1:17:00.60,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,1960年时，有一百万只野生黑猩猩
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.40,1:17:09.90,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,如今仅剩下1/15
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.90,1:17:25.40,BLC-50,,0,0,0,,在这里你将知道如何帮忙
